      "correct_choice_id": 5,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Zce79039ee0c9c756b2e006d3be169afc\" data-sememe-id=\"IL0Y_g\">Vaccination</a> is used for prevention, not treatment of active infection. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Zccf40214e7861046a572df429ee6e389\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Zccf40214e7861046a572df429ee6e389\" data-section-id=\"QxbuwD\" data-sememe-id=\"MIcMWd0\">Yellow fever vaccine</a> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=_m05Rg&anker=Z6fc03b2f7d1e14fe5c476f3ce29d80f8\" data-learningcard-id=\"_m05Rg\" data-anker=\"Z6fc03b2f7d1e14fe5c476f3ce29d80f8\" data-section-id=\"uRcpKX0\" data-sememe-id=\"XdY9oL\">live-attenuated vaccine</a> that is contraindicated in any patient with an acute moderate or severe illness. This patient has established <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-sememe-id=\"8L0Ozg\">yellow fever</a> infection requiring symptomatic management.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span data-sememe-id=\"xWbEns\">Liver biopsy</span> is contraindicated in active <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-sememe-id=\"8L0Ozg\">yellow fever</a> infection as it may result in life-threatening hemorrhage, especially in patients with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=wT0hG2&anker=Zdab14a350ac311c7a2589ab7d48358ad\" data-learningcard-id=\"wT0hG2\" data-anker=\"Zdab14a350ac311c7a2589ab7d48358ad\" data-sememe-id=\"sP0tTT\">thrombocytopenia</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=8T0Os2&anker=Z5a3cc6f90267ccb75d4d2c02be76da5a\" data-learningcard-id=\"8T0Os2\" data-anker=\"Z5a3cc6f90267ccb75d4d2c02be76da5a\" data-sememe-id=\"7P04TT\">coagulopathy</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Z77eab8ad21e1df2528da6877600391d8\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Z77eab8ad21e1df2528da6877600391d8\" data-section-id=\"w7bhLE\" data-sememe-id=\"piaLs4\">Ibuprofen</a> and other <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-section-id=\"0kcemc0\" data-sememe-id=\"riafG4\">NSAIDs</a> are contraindicated in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-sememe-id=\"8L0Ozg\">yellow fever</a> as they increase bleeding risk. This <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=FI0geh&anker=Z5bae7c27e3a0c0cf9dca623faff79c19\" data-learningcard-id=\"FI0geh\" data-anker=\"Z5bae7c27e3a0c0cf9dca623faff79c19\" data-section-id=\"Ul1bwS0\" data-sememe-id=\"Hc1Kdf0\">patient presentation</a> indicates hemorrhagic complications with black vomit and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=8T0Os2&anker=Z5a3cc6f90267ccb75d4d2c02be76da5a\" data-learningcard-id=\"8T0Os2\" data-anker=\"Z5a3cc6f90267ccb75d4d2c02be76da5a\" data-sememe-id=\"7P04TT\">coagulopathy</a>, making <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-section-id=\"0kcemc0\" data-sememe-id=\"riafG4\">NSAIDs</a> particularly dangerous.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>No specific antiviral treatment is available for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-sememe-id=\"8L0Ozg\">yellow fever</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pm0Lgg&anker=Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-learningcard-id=\"pm0Lgg\" data-anker=\"Z18a8b3fbdf430fc0b02a7a0b68ddcfd3\" data-section-id=\"wBXh100\" data-sememe-id=\"FWYgML\">Ribavirin</a> is not effective against <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Pn0Wtg&anker=Zee4c28b0343a924585ff55b7c5aaac6a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Pn0Wtg\" data-anker=\"Zee4c28b0343a924585ff55b7c5aaac6a\" data-section-id=\"2acTPa0\">yellow fever virus</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) CORRECT:</h4>Correct -- <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=U50bjg&anker=Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"U50bjg\" data-anker=\"Z93dc20aca790221499cf385e2b0e7b8e\" data-sememe-id=\"8L0Ozg\">Yellow fever</a> management is entirely supportive, focusing on maintaining fluid and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"-mYDRp\">electrolyte</a> balance, adequate nutrition, and replacing blood components lost to hemorrhage. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Za3da7a7c0e6eb1d1d781615b1c2c7af3\" data-section-id=\"Ykcnmc0\" data-sememe-id=\"gvYFzI\">Acetaminophen</a> is safe for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> control, unlike <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=BN0zWg&anker=Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-learningcard-id=\"BN0zWg\" data-anker=\"Z6d53b6cfe3376a70645a5c797293e56a\" data-section-id=\"0kcemc0\" data-sememe-id=\"riafG4\">NSAIDs</a>, which increase bleeding risk. The patient shows signs of progression to the period of intoxication with hemorrhagic complications.</div>",
